ers; all over Norrath we see the kindness and generosity of players.  That is why we are asking you and members of your guild to join us on this very special day of remembrance: it is an opportunity for all of us to spread kindness, support, and healing in the wake of last week's terrible tragedy.<br><br>This type of event is easy to organize and costs nothing but time.  You can set up a buffing station in a zone where your guild currently likes to congregate, or head to a newbie starting zone with some food, drink, and maybe some level-appropriate items a newbie would greatly appreciate, like low-end weapons and patchwork armor.  Whatever you choose, remember, it's the thought that counts.<br><br>If you have questions, or need assistance setting up an event for your guild, please feel free to contact us at eqrandomacts@hotmail.com, or see our Events, Hunting, and Gathering board at <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub76.ezboard.com/brandomacts.">pub76.ezboard.com/brandomacts.</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>Please join us as we offer our thoughts and hopes to the victims, their families, and their friends at this difficult time.<br><br>On behalf of Random Acts of Morell-Thule,<br><br>Gwion Llewellyn, Random Acts Events Coordinator<br>Hamadryad Long, Guild Founder<br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.eqrandomacts.com">www.eqrandomacts.com</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>eqrandomacts@hotmail.com<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsevents.showPrevMessage?topicID=253.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsevents.showNextMessage?topicID=253.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsevents.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=253.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/th